item.description:

well its not the smartest plan… but:
1.copy and paste everything you’ve edited into one folder and put in on your background.
2.delete hiyascape v2
3.download hiyascapev2 again.
4.paste all you’re edited files into that new folder you just downloaded.
try this.i know alot to get one thing back but it’ll be worth it i think.
